{"tid":1811954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣疾管署檢疫發現8名武漢旅客發燒","createTime":"2020-01-05T07:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T11:52:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":324,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"0187bd4056cd59acd2a121851cc797fd8642d49f","tid":1811954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】台灣當局因應武漢不明肺炎疫情，對武漢直航班機啟動檢疫措施，至今發現8名旅客發燒，全部徵狀輕微。<br />\n<br />\n台灣疾管署自上周四起，針對武漢直航班機派員逐班登機檢疫，在檢查的8班機、740多名旅客中，發現8名旅客發燒，醫生評估風險低後，獲准回家休息，其中5人就醫後，分別確診流感及支氣管炎等，其餘3人、當局會繼續追蹤。除了登機檢疫外，疾管署亦要求醫院報告到過武漢旅遊的肺炎患者，至今未有收到通報。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14672&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=a58dcea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14672&h=a6bd6958\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14672</a>"},{"pid":"61cddfc6795d8e782eb9065d1d968b2031565f8c","tid":1811954,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"797f70cfc50cbcdf3cb058a4bf8e646381846d88","tid":1811954,"uid":128731,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"支那式攬炒"},{"pid":"ce731cbc58daba022bdcbb8ea9fe774038e0753c","tid":1811954,"uid":199712,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"屌你咩支那又送大禮"},{"pid":"66b5c225e6b3a7eba5f7224b4826753d2e5bdf47","tid":1811954,"uid":54511,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"好明顯真係有心 張 病毒擴散去全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f23d6ef8236ece44171d943b374099e1258040e","tid":1811954,"uid":46042,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTim